WEBVTT

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:01.694
and they'd eventually touch the snake.

00:04:02.575 --> 00:04:07.179
And when they touched the snake,
everything was fine. They were cured.

00:04:07.203 --> 00:04:09.323
In fact, everything was better than fine.

00:04:09.347 --> 00:04:12.600
These people who had
lifelong fears of snakes

00:04:13.219 --> 00:04:14.729
were saying things like,

00:04:15.396 --> 00:04:17.374
"Look how beautiful that snake is."

00:04:17.398 --> 00:04:20.513
And they were holding it in their laps.

00:04:21.673 --> 00:04:25.226
Bandura calls this process
"guided mastery."

00:04:25.582 --> 00:04:28.169
I love that term: guided mastery.

00:04:29.081 --> 00:04:30.761
And something else happened.